description:
asian-role

Welcome to asian-role model, this is a Chinese gorgeous antique style game role model. This model is intended to produce high-quality, highly detailed anime style with just a few prompts.

e.g. 1girl, white hair, beautiful blue eyes, red lips, detailed sky, garden

This model is a merged model, it has GuoFeng3 and Chilloutmix in it.
